      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-07-02T03:40:24Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So this is actually a map from an ordered list of StructParent Keys (the index, to which some base is added to create the key) to the nodeIds which reference them. From these StructParent Keys the ParentTree is created.\n\nIt seems that different StructParent Keys which pointed to the same node would all be identical mappings.",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 412,
        "startChar": 27,
        "endLine": 412,
        "endChar": 55
      },
      "revId": "02084f4915b745c369f98a29ab1097b8d53048cf",
